    "metaTitle": "eCommerce Fashion Marketplace Platform — UK Multi-Brand Retailer — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK multi-brand fashion retailer with 340 independent designer brands, 2.4 million registered customers, and ...",
    "sector": "eCommerce / Fashion Marketplace",
