    "metaTitle": "RetailTech UK Department Store Digital Transformation — Omnichannel — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK heritage department store with 28 stores, £840M annual revenue, 4.2M loyalty cardholders, and an aging Or...",
    "sector": "RetailTech / Omnichannel",
