    "writtenBy": "ClickMasters Case Study Team",
    "reviewedBy": "James Whitmore, CTO</p></td></tr></table><p>Home › Case Studies › <strong>FinTech Open Banking Personal Finance Management — UK Consumer App</strong></p><h1><strong>FinTech Open Banking Personal Finance Management — UK Consumer App</strong></h1><table><tr><td><p><strong>🏭 FinTech / Personal Finance</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>🇬🇧 UK</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>✅ On Time</strong></p></td><td><p><strong>📋 Fixed Price</strong></p></td></tr></table><table><tr><td><p>Sector: FinTech / Personal Finance"
