    "metaTitle": "FinTech SME Challenger Bank — UK FCA Authorised Embedded Finance — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK FCA-authorised neobank targeting SME businesses (sole traders, Ltd companies, and partnerships) with 84,0...",
    "sector": "FinTech / SME Banking",
