    "title": "GovTech NHS Workforce Management Platform -- NHS England",
    "metaTitle": "GovTech NHS Workforce Management Platform -- NHS England -- ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "An NHS England programme needed to modernise workforce management for 280,000 NHS staff across 84 trusts in on...",
    "sector": "",
