    "title": "FinTech Open Banking PFM App -- FCA and Consumer Duty",
    "metaTitle": "FinTech Open Banking PFM App -- FCA and Consumer Duty -- ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "UK FinTech building Personal Finance Management app (iOS + Android, 280,000 users year one) using Open Banking...",
