    "slug": "insurtech-legal-expenses-insurance-claims",
    "title": "InsurTech UK Legal Expenses Insurance Claims Platform",
    "metaTitle": "InsurTech UK Legal Expenses Insurance Claims Platform -- ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK FCA-authorised Legal Expenses Insurance (LEI) provider (280,000 policies, GBP42M gross written premium) n...",
