    "technology": "Next.js 14, Node.js, TypeScript, PostgreSQL, TrueLayer Open Banking, Stripe, AWS eu-west-2, Terraform, GitHub Actions | Compliance: UK GDPR Article 28, FCA Consumer Duty UX compliance, ICO registration, Cyber Essentials",
    "compliance": "UK GDPR Article 28, FCA Consumer Duty UX compliance, ICO registration, Cyber Essentials",
