    "results": "Launched to 500 beta users at 7 months — 1 month ahead of FCA deadline. FCA Consumer Duty audit at 6 months: zero adverse findings. KYC pass rate: 87% automated approval (13% referred for manual review). Faster Payments: average settlement 8 seconds. Beta NPS: 67 (industry benchmark: 30). Funded Series A at £8.5M within 3 months of beta launch.",
