    "title": "AI-Powered Document Intelligence — UK Law Firm",
    "metaTitle": "AI-Powered Document Intelligence — UK Law Firm — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK mid-market law firm with 180 fee earners spent an average of 3.2 hours per transaction on document review...",
