    "slug": "supply-chain-visibility-fmcg",
    "title": "Supply Chain Visibility Platform — UK FMCG Manufacturer",
    "metaTitle": "Supply Chain Visibility Platform — UK FMCG Manufacturer — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK FMCG manufacturer producing 340 product SKUs across 4 factories needed real-time supply chain visibility ...",
