    "title": "AI-Powered Compliance Monitoring — UK FCA-Regulated FinTech",
    "metaTitle": "AI-Powered Compliance Monitoring — UK FCA-Regulated FinTech — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK FCA-regulated payments company processing 2.4M transactions per month needed to replace manual transactio...",
