    "title": "HealthTech Clinical Decision Support — UK Oncology Centre",
    "metaTitle": "HealthTech Clinical Decision Support — UK Oncology Centre — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK cancer centre treating 4,200 patients per year wanted to build a clinical decision support (CDS) tool for...",
