    "title": "EdTech Adaptive Learning Platform — UK GCSE Revision App",
    "metaTitle": "EdTech Adaptive Learning Platform — UK GCSE Revision App — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK EdTech startup wanted to build an adaptive learning platform for GCSE revision — serving Year 10 and Year...",
    "sector": "EdTech / Consumer",
