    "metaTitle": "CleanTech Renewable Energy Monitoring Platform — UK Offshore Wind Operator — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK offshore wind operator managing 48 turbines needed to replace 3 separate monitoring systems (SCADA data, ...",
