    "title": "RegTech Automated Regulatory Reporting — UK Asset Manager",
    "metaTitle": "RegTech Automated Regulatory Reporting — UK Asset Manager — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK FCA-authorised asset manager with £2.1B AUM was spending 3 days per month manually compiling FCA regulato...",
    "sector": "RegTech / Asset Management",
