    "title": "EduTech Learning Analytics Platform — UK Multi-Academy Trust",
    "metaTitle": "EduTech Learning Analytics Platform — UK Multi-Academy Trust — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK Multi-Academy Trust (MAT) with 18 schools and 9,400 pupils needed a learning analytics platform to aggreg...",
