    "title": "FinTech Crypto Tax Reporting Platform — UK Individual Investors",
    "metaTitle": "FinTech Crypto Tax Reporting Platform — UK Individual Investors — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK FinTech startup wanted to build a cryptocurrency tax reporting platform for UK individual investors. UK H...",
