    "title": "HealthTech Mental Health App — NHS Talking Therapies Integration",
    "metaTitle": "HealthTech Mental Health App — NHS Talking Therapies Integration — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK digital mental health company wanted to build a self-guided CBT (Cognitive Behavioural Therapy) app for m...",
    "sector": "HealthTech / Mental Health",
