    "title": "PropTech Conveyancing Automation — UK Law Firm",
    "metaTitle": "PropTech Conveyancing Automation — UK Law Firm — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK conveyancing law firm completing 4,200 property transactions per year wanted to automate their conveyanci...",
    "sector": "PropTech / LegalTech",
