    "metaTitle": "LegalTech IP Management Platform — UK Patent Attorney Firm — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK patent attorney firm managing 4,800 active patent and trademark cases across 60 jurisdictions needed to r...",
    "sector": "LegalTech / IP Management",
