    "metaTitle": "FinTech RegTech Compliance Monitoring Platform — UK Compliance Consultancy — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "A UK FCA-authorised compliance consultancy providing outsourced compliance services to 85 FCA-regulated firms ...",
