    "metaTitle": "HealthTech NHS Mental Health Crisis Pathway — Trust Digital Triage — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "An NHS Mental Health Trust with a 24/7 crisis line (1,400 calls/month) needed to build a digital crisis triage...",
    "sector": "HealthTech / Mental Health",
    "country": "UK",
    "status": "On Time",
