    "title": "GovTech NHS Secondary Care Referral Platform — Integrated Care Board",
    "metaTitle": "GovTech NHS Secondary Care Referral Platform — Integrated Care Board — ClickMasters Case Study",
    "metaDesc": "An NHS Integrated Care Board managing secondary care referrals for a population of 680,000 people wanted to re...",
    "sector": "GovTech / NHS Referrals",
